Package: linkedCells
Type: Package
Title: Reactive Cell Linking for Editable Shiny Tables
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Indranil", "Gayen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nil.gayen@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Indranil Gayen <nil.gayen@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for building interactive editable tables in Shiny with
    linked cell behaviour. Users can define rules that update dependent
    cells when values are modified. Supports asynchronous computation,
    batch editing, and reactive updates across cells.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    shiny,
    DT,
    future,
    promises,
    shinyjs,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    openxlsx,
    readxl,
    later
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
